dct_title_s: State of New Jersey Board of Commerce and Navigation map showing pierhead and bulkhead line applied for by New York Dock Department at hearing held Nov. 3, 1921
dct_description_sm: Map of Hudson River and Spuyten Duyvil Creek indicating the location where the pierhead and bulkhead line was applied for by the New York Dock Department at a hearing held November 3, 1921
